  "contentHtml": "<!-- BEGIN COPYRIGHTED TEXT CHUNK --><html><head></head><body><dl class=\"bookList\">\n\t\n<!-- html_article_summary.inc.php -->\n\n<dt><a href=\"/authors/ontl/bl131\" id=\"bl131\">Of Mindsets and Monkeypots</a>, \n<span class=\"by\">by  Petr Karel Ontl</span>\n<span class=\"filedata\">(2005; 10pp./29KB)</span>\n<a class=\"imgLink\" href=\"./bl131.pdf\" title=\"Get the pdf version (??pages/111KB)\"><img src=\"/img/pdf_24x18.gif\" alt=\"[PDF icon]\" height=\"16\"></a>  </dt>\n<dd>Three short essays on elementary Buddhist practice: \"Of Mindsets and Monkeypots\" (on letting go); \"Does the Dhamma Still Hold True?\" (on the relevance of Dhamma practice in the modern age); \"In Search of Happiness\" (on how to seek a true and lasting happiness). </dd>\n\n</dl>\n\n\n</body></html>",
